---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Nav from '../components/Nav.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';

const lastUpdated = 'April 19, 2026';
---

<Layout title="Terms of Service — Ultiplay" description="Terms governing use of the Ultiplay website.">
	<Nav />

	<main class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-6 py-20 md:py-28">
		<header>
			<p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-fuchsia-300">Legal</p>
			<h1 class="mt-3 text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white sm:text-5xl">Terms of Service</h1>
			<p class="mt-3 text-sm text-slate-500">Last updated: {lastUpdated}</p>
		</header>

		<div class="mt-12 space-y-8 text-slate-300">
			<section>
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">1. Acceptance</h2>
				<p class="mt-3">
					By accessing or using this website ("the Site"), you agree to these Terms of Service.
					If you do not agree, please do not use the Site. The Ultiplay desktop application is
					governed by a separate End User License Agreement (EULA) included with the installer.
				</p>
			</section>

			<section>
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">2. About Ultiplay</h2>
				<p class="mt-3">
					Ultiplay is a multi-video player application for Microsoft Windows. This Site provides
					information about the product, a launch waitlist, and — once available — purchase links
					processed by our payments partner, Lemon Squeezy.
				</p>
			</section>

			<section>
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">3. Permitted use</h2>
				<p class="mt-3">
					You may browse the Site for personal or commercial evaluation. You may not:
				</p>
				<ul class="mt-3 list-disc space-y-2 pl-6">
					<li>scrape, crawl, or systematically harvest content beyond reasonable indexing;</li>
					<li>attempt to disrupt, attack, or reverse-engineer the Site or its hosting infrastructure;</li>
					<li>impersonate Ultiplay or use our branding or assets in a misleading way.</li>
				</ul>
			</section>

			<section>
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">4. Intellectual property</h2>
				<p class="mt-3">
					All Site content — including the Ultiplay name, logo, copy, artwork, the commercial
					video, and product screenshots — is owned by us or our licensors and is protected by
					copyright and trademark law. You may not reproduce or redistribute this material without
					prior written permission, except for normal browsing and fair use commentary.
				</p>
			</section>

			<section>
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">5. Waitlist signup</h2>
				<p class="mt-3">
					You may submit your email address to be notified about Ultiplay's launch. By doing so,
					you consent to receive a small number of launch-related emails. You can unsubscribe or
					request deletion at any time — see our
					<a href="/privacy" class="text-fuchsia-300 underline hover:text-fuchsia-200">Privacy Policy</a>.
				</p>
			</section>

			<section>
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">6. Purchases and licensing</h2>
				<p class="mt-3">
					When Ultiplay becomes purchasable, all transactions are processed by Lemon Squeezy, who
					also issues your license key. Refunds, billing, and tax handling are governed by Lemon
					Squeezy's policies as well as the Ultiplay EULA delivered with the application. Pricing
					is subject to change; the price displayed at checkout is the price you pay.
				</p>
			</section>

			<section>
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">7. Disclaimers</h2>
				<p class="mt-3">
					The Site is provided "as is" without warranties of any kind, express or implied,
					including merchantability, fitness for a particular purpose, and non-infringement. We
					make no guarantees about uptime, accuracy, or availability of the Site or any specific
					feature of the application.
				</p>
			</section>

			<section>
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">8. Limitation of liability</h2>
				<p class="mt-3">
					To the fullest extent permitted by law, Ultiplay shall not be liable for any indirect,
					incidental, special, consequential, or punitive damages arising from your use of the
					Site. Our total liability for any claim relating to the Site is limited to the amount
					you paid (if any) for access to the Site.
				</p>
			</section>

			<section>
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">9. Third-party content</h2>
				<p class="mt-3">
					The Site embeds third-party content (e.g. YouTube videos) and links to third-party
					services (e.g. Lemon Squeezy). We are not responsible for the content, policies, or
					practices of those third parties.
				</p>
			</section>

			<section>
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">10. Changes</h2>
				<p class="mt-3">
					We may update these Terms from time to time. The "Last updated" date will reflect the
					change. Continued use of the Site after a change constitutes acceptance of the revised
					Terms.
				</p>
			</section>

			<section>
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">11. Contact</h2>
				<p class="mt-3">
					Questions? Email
					<a href="mailto:support@ultiplay.net" class="text-fuchsia-300 underline hover:text-fuchsia-200">support@ultiplay.net</a>.
				</p>
			</section>
		</div>
	</main>

	<Footer />
</Layout>
